  "prompt": "What is best institute in Hyderabad for group 2 exams?",
  "response": "As of my last update in October 2023, several well-regarded institutes in Hyderabad offer coaching for Group 2 exams, particularly for candidates preparing for state-level public service exams like the Telangana State Public Service Commission (TSPSC) Group 2 exams. Some of the reputed institutes include:\n\n1. **Sri Chaitanya Institute** - Known for its structured coaching programs and experienced faculty.\n2. **Sharada IAS Academy** - Offers comprehensive coaching and has a good track record of success.\n3. **Vishnu Academy** - Provides focused preparation for various competitive exams, including Group 2.\n4. **KSG India** - Offers classes for public service examinations and has a good reputation among aspirants.\n5. **Sankalp IAS Academy** - Focuses on Group 2 exam preparation with a tailored curriculum.\n\nIt's essential to visit these institutes, check their course offerings, faculty qualifications, teaching methodologies, and success rates to find the one that best fits your needs. Additionally, consider seeking feedback from current or former students to make an informed decision.",
